item.description:
<![CDATA[Gadwal: The 162nd birth anniversary of Swami Vivekananda was celebrated grandly today under the aegis of the All-Party Committee at the Ieeja Municipality Center in Jogulamba Gadwal district.
Speaking on the occasion, the speakers emphasized that the youth of this country should draw inspiration from Swami Vivekananda's ideals.
